document_data.mainbody:
Sharp-eye Nass was a goblin scout and a member of the camp that followed the faithful of the Absolute and dwelled within the Shattered Sanctum during the late 15 century DR.
As one of her goblin camps sharp-eyes, Nass acted as a scout working under Skrut.
Nass was among the raiders that burned down Waukeens Rest in the . While Nass endured an injured arm, she managed to make it back to the Shattered Sanctum alive.
